description:
In Italy were published 2 different series of Mafia: the numbering started over again with the second one. Here, the issues are proposed by series/number (for example, II/05 means number 5 of the II.nd series).

For the first series, Edifumetto published 63 issues, from 06-1979 to 08-1984 and 2 supplements (#I/13suppl. - Naufragio, and #I/26suppl. - I traditori pagano); for the second series 14 issues from 11-1984 to 12-1985 and 1 supplement (#II/09suppl. - I tentacoli della mafia). In 1986, another story is published as a supplement in the series "Super Poliziotta" (#9suppl. - MAFIA - La strage degli innocenti).

The first series is about the criminal adventures of mobster Johnny "Baby" Lupano, while the second series has no recurring character.
name: Mafia
